sourcesContent:
import React from 'react'; function CreateResume({ data }) { const { name, email, phone, experience, education, skills } = data; return (

Resume Preview

Personal Information

Name: {name}

Email: {email}

Phone: {phone}

Experience

{experience.map((exp, index) => (

Job Title: {exp.jobTitle}

Company: {exp.company}

Start Date: {exp.startDate}

End Date: {exp.endDate}

Description: {exp.description}

))}

Education

{education.map((edu, index) => (

Degree: {edu.degree}

Field: {edu.field}

University: {edu.university}

Year: {edu.year}

))}

Skills

{skills.join(', ')}

); } export default CreateResume;
